[section#optional.dtor
    [:en] Destructor
    [:zh_CN] 析构函数
]

[%@lib@dtor optional]
[codeblock:declaration]
constexpr ~optional();
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] If [`is_trivially_destructible_v<T>] is [`false] and [`*this] contains a
value, calls [`[*val].T::~T()].
[:zh_CN] 若 [`is_trivially_destructible_v<T>] 为 [`false] 且 [`*this] 包含值，
则调用 [`[*val].T::~T()]。

[para:remarks]
[:en] If [`is_trivially_destructible_v<T>] is [`true], then this destructor is trivial.
[:zh_CN] 若 [`is_trivially_destructible_v<T>] 为 [`true]，则这个析构函数为平凡的。
[div:end]
